   Parvin, Hamid, Islamic Azad Univ, Nourabad Mamasani Branch, Young Researchers \& Elite Club, Nourabad Mamasani, Iran.
   Rezaie, Vahideh, Islamic Azad Univ, Yasooj Branch, Dept Math, Yasuj, Iran.},
