   ensemble learning; Multi -objective ensemble pruning; Multimodal
   perturbation; Adaptive combination},
Keywords-Plus = {GAUSSIAN PROCESS REGRESSION; SOFT SENSOR DEVELOPMENT; TIME DIFFERENCE;
   ERROR-CORRECTION; NEURAL-NETWORK; MODEL; SPEED; PREDICTION;
