   Oliveira, Luiz S., Fed Univ Parana UFPR, Dept Informat, Curitiba, Parana, Brazil.
   Koerich, Alessandro L.; Sabourin, Robert, Univ Quebec, ETS, Montreal, PQ H3C 3P8, Canada.},
